        frq: { type: "Related Rates FRQ", prompt: "Water drains from a conical tank at 2 m³/min. The tank has height 10m and radius 5m at the top. Find how fast the water level drops when water is 6m deep. Show complete setup.", rubricTip: "The setup earns as many points as the answer. Write the volume equation, differentiate with respect to t, substitute known values — each step is a potential rubric point. A wrong answer with correct method still earns partial credit." },
